<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正好想帶你去個地方，<delay40 />
現在就跟我一起走吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />其實我一直在這裡
偷偷地等<tag a="110" b="4" />喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來，<delay20 />現在就跟我走吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />幸好我有待在這裡等你，<delay40 />
本來還在想沒等到你的話，該怎麼辦呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我現在
很想帶你去一個地方唷。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就什麼都別問，跟我來吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 06 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><tag a="10" b="6" /><size value="150" />生日～～<delay8 />快～樂～～！！<size value="100" /><endTag a="10" b="6" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我們大家想給你一個驚喜，
所以就偷偷地決定<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />幫你辦個慶生會了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生日蛋糕也準備好了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你能不能按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />，呼地吹一口氣，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把蠟燭吹熄呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，為了幫你慶生，
大家還一起準備了派對喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是覺得很驚喜呀？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay20 />因為今年不是閏年，<delay20 />
所以派對舉辦得比你的生日早了一點。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你能玩得開心！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來吧！<delay20 />在派對正式開始前，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要先把蛋糕上的蠟燭吹熄才行，<delay20 />
你只要按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />就可以吹蠟燭囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對<tag a="110" b="4" />來說，
今天是四年才過一次的生日吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟是這麼特別的生日嘛。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們就想辦個慶生會，給你一個驚喜，
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />本來是想嚇你一跳的，<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，只要你玩得開心就好。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我們<delay20 />就趕快開始吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你只要按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />把蠟燭吹熄，<delay20 />
派對就正式開始囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀！<delay40 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！
你要去哪裡呀～？<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要先把蠟燭吹熄才行喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay40 />等一下啦～！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你忘記<delay8 />要把蠟燭吹熄了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />你要去哪裡呢？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天你可是派對的主角，<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有蛋糕在等著你喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
生日快樂！</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我為你精心準備了<delay8 />
很特別的禮物喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />你願意收下嗎？</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望今天對你來說，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />會是難忘的一天！</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />至於裡面裝的是什麼，
就是拆禮物時的樂趣了。<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望這個禮物<delay20 />對你來說還算實用<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />啊，<delay20 />對了對了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天還有另一個<delay20 />
大家一起送你的禮物呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我先去準備一下，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以請你在這裡等一下嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀呀<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你真是的，<delay20 />
包包都已經滿到裝不下禮物了嘛！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣好了，
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我晚點再把這個生日禮物<delay20 />送到你家吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實今天還有一個<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家一起送給你的禮物呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我去準備一下，<delay20 />你在這裡等等喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看看天花板！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是大家用心為你做的皮納塔喔！</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那裡面裝著我們想送給<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />的一點小禮物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在就拿棒子給你，<delay20 />
請盡力敲破皮納塔吧！</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />敲的時機由<tag a="110" b="4" />決定，<delay20 />
如果你做好心理準備了，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就跟我說一聲吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀！<delay8 />想挑戰看看了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay8 />感覺真讓人興奮呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就請你<delay8 />移動到皮納塔前面，
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />準備開始吧。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這畢竟是我們精心製作的皮納塔，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果只是隨便敲幾下，可是敲不破的喔～<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />敲皮納塔的秘訣就是<delay8 />快速連續的敲擊！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當我一喊<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「開始」的時候！<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就要拼命地<delay20 />連按<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />鍵唷！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼<delay8 />要開始囉<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
預～備<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開始！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="025" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />成功敲破了耶！<delay40 />
你很擅長敲皮納塔嘛。<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡面裝的是<colour id="1" />生日紙杯蛋糕<colour id="65535" />喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你很會敲皮納塔呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能漂亮地敲破它，真是太好了。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />裡面裝的是<colour id="1" />生日紙杯蛋糕<colour id="65535" />喔。<delay40 />
這是大家各自帶材料來一起做的，<delay40 />
希望能合你的口味，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />你好厲害喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道你很常敲皮納塔嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為你剛才的動作看起來很專業呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />順帶一提，這個皮納塔裡面<delay20 />
裝的是<colour id="1" />生日紙杯蛋糕<colour id="65535" />喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你會喜歡這個口味，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="028" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來，<delay8 />請不要客氣，<delay20 />
儘管收下<colour id="1" />生日紙杯蛋糕<colour id="65535" />吧。</message>
	<message label="029" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我們做了很多蛋糕，<delay20 />
所以拿去分給今天沒辦法來的朋友<delay20 />
也許是個好點子呢。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說回來<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天你的持有物品已經滿了吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那紙杯蛋糕
我會幫你先送到家裡的。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay40 />
你的包包已經滿了，<delay20 />
裝不下更多東西了喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我看這個紙杯蛋糕，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等一下我再幫你寄到家裡好了。</message>
	<message label="032" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好了！<delay20 />
生日驚喜活動<delay8 />舉辦成功！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到你敲皮納塔的樣子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得<delay8 />感動到眼淚都要流出來了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />島上的大家一起準備驚喜<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也值得了。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay8 />接下來就請你盡情地<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />享受派對吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="033" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />你要回去了吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天真的很高興你能來。<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明年的生日，你也要好好期待喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="035" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等、<delay20 />等一下！<delay20 />你現在就要回去了！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />至少先敲了皮納塔<delay8 />
再回去嘛！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="036" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等、<delay8 />等等！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你把皮納塔和我們丟在這裡，<delay20 />
要去哪裡呀！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="037" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你沒看見天花板上的皮納塔嗎！？<delay frames="40" />
<delay8 />拜託你<delay8 />回來這裡嘛！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要吹熄蠟燭的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
「呼～」地吹一口氣就可以了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來，<delay8 />快點按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />把蠟燭吹熄吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家都期待這一刻<delay8 />
好久了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得燭光熄滅的瞬間，
很讓人雀躍呢。<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為這可是生日派對中的重頭戲之一嘛。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不用著急沒關係，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />先深深吸一口氣，<delay20 />然後按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
呼地吹熄蠟燭吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />敲皮納塔真的很好玩呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我記得這個遊戲是從<delay20 />
敲打惡魔的驅魔習俗演變而來的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想<tag a="110" b="4" />
既然能順利敲破皮納塔，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那肯定連惡魔都能打贏吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在房間裡布置完生日的裝飾後，<delay20 />
看起來就完全不一樣了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果一整年都住在這樣的房間，<delay20 />
肯定每天都像在開派對一樣，
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說不定也很有趣呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />皮納塔裡面好像都會<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />裝糖果或點心的樣子。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想裝些不一樣的東西<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
我想文具或護手霜，<delay20 />
還有遊樂園的入場券都不錯喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
今天的生日派對的主角是你喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要玩得盡興再走！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />敲破皮納塔的那瞬間，
感覺心情特別暢快呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不曉得皮納塔什麼時候會被敲破這一點，
也讓人覺得很刺激，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>